  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Last edit about 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n29\nNeeds Review\n29\n68 tempore that Eliade speaks of. Then it wasn't the past breaking into the present; it was the sacred breaking into the profane. Sacred world + sacred (actions) (then the 11-17-80 theophany drama was probably also genuine.) This is what I mean speak of seeing world under the aspect of when I of \"Parsifal.\" The \"eidos\" was a sacred Act III the last time that the savior was here. Then in one. this the AI voice + its prophecies take on",
